      value: Sign
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _signText
      value: This is a test lolololol
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _textBoxDisplayer
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1497152694}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _signText.Array.size
      value: 7
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_signText.Array.data[0]'
      value: If you're reading this newbie (I hope you are), then welcome to the
        training grounds.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_signText.Array.data[1]'
      value: I have this made to simulate what it would be like as a Package Creature
        Trainer in the real world.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_signText.Array.data[2]'
      value: Anyways, to get your Inpup, you wanna press ESC and then click the "Generate
        Package Creature" button.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_signText.Array.data[3]'
      value: Then enter either "Input System", or the internal name for the package
        there. That's the package Inpup's based off if it wasn't obvious.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_signText.Array.data[4]'
      value: Just click confirm after that and your all good to go.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_signText.Array.data[5]'
      value: Right, now go get on it. You've got a simulated incident you need to
        resolve ahead of you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8390838681701955729, guid: 01dca9bb37127b8409379e2530153558, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_signText.Array.data[6]'
      value: End text
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
